<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Escolha suas Agendas - WhatsCalendar</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #00E676;
            --primary-dark: #00C853;
            --accent: #2979FF;
            --bg: #F4F7FE;
            --text-dark: #2B3674;
            --text-gray: #A3AED0;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #F4F7FE 0%, #E2EDF8 100%);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(112, 144, 176, 0.12);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--primary));
        }

        h1 { 
            font-weight: 700; 
            font-size: 22px; 
            margin-bottom: 12px; 
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        p { 
            color: var(--text-gray); 
            font-size: 14px; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
        }

        .calendar-list {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-height: 300px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 10px;
        }

        .calendar-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #F4F7FE;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .calendar-item:hover {
            background: #E2EDF8;
        }

        .calendar-item input[type="checkbox"] {
            margin-right: 15px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            accent-color: var(--primary);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .calendar-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .calendar-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .calendar-email {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.2);
        }

        button:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.3);
        }

        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        .calendar-list::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        .calendar-list::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #F4F7FE;
        }
        .calendar-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--text-gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Quais agendas deseja monitorar?</h1>
        <p>Selecione as agendas que você quer que o WhatsCalendar envie para você todos os dias.</p>
        
        <form action="/save-calendars" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="whatsappNumber" value="<%= whatsappNumber %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="preferredTime" value="<%= preferredTime %>">
            
            <div class="calendar-list">
                <% calendars.forEach(cal => { %>
                    <label class="calendar-item">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="selectedCalendars" value="<%= cal.id %>" <%= cal.primary ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                        <div class="calendar-info">
                            <span class="calendar-name"><%= cal.summary %></span>
                            <span class="calendar-email"><%= cal.id %></span>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit">Finalizar Configuração</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
